te;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>總是亂咬東西、咬垃圾迎接我們回家</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/e1596/omupast2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"omu past\"\n        title=\"omu past\"\n        src=\"/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/1c72d/omupast2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/a80bd/omupast2.jpg 148w,\n/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/1c91a/omupast2.jpg 295w,\n/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/1c72d/omupast2.jpg 590w,\n/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/a8a14/omupast2.jpg 885w,\n/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/fbd2c/omupast2.jpg 1180w,\n/static/f6b9a70423ec0abc645bae7b9a26feaf/e1596/omupast2.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>我追你跑的戲碼不斷上演⋯</p>\n<p>我們都拿你沒辦法，溫柔勸說、嚴厲告誡都沒有用，</p>\n<p>只能在我們出門時，讓你待在籠子裡</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/e1596/omupast3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"omu past\"\n        title=\"omu past\"\n        src=\"/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/1c72d/omupast3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/a80bd/omupast3.jpg 148w,\n/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/1c91a/omupast3.jpg 295w,\n/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/1c72d/omupast3.jpg 590w,\n/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/a8a14/omupast3.jpg 885w,\n/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/fbd2c/omupast3.jpg 1180w,\n/static/27ef8913add56ab53d1c741bb2f9bbf7/e1596/omupast3.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>回家時，常常看到你把自己弄得濕答答，我知道你不喜歡被關，肯定又是激動掙扎時把水盆弄倒潑到自己了</p>\n<p>所以我們一回到家總是先幫你把身體吹乾，安慰你受傷的小心靈</p>\n<p>你也總是很快就展開笑容在我們後面當跟屁蟲，走到哪跟到哪</p>\n<p>一年很快就過去了  </p>\n<p><br/><br/></p>\n<p>室友窯是我們當中最忙碌的一位，第二忙是室友魚，常常需要在學校做實驗到很晚</p>\n<p>所以我們決定搬去離學校更近的套房，只能兩人住一間（離學校越近，房租越高啊。。。</p>\n<p>當時大三了</p>\n<p>我沒特別選什麼課，所以課表極空</p>\n<p>大部分的時間都跟歐姆一起廢在家</p>\n<p>傍晚帶歐姆去校園走走，認識新朋友</p>\n<p>還遇到另一隻同類臘腸叫阿福</p>\n<p><br/><br/></p>\n<p>學校附近有一間獸醫，我超怕那個醫生，因為他好兇。。。</p>\n<p>可能他嗅出我這個養狗新手的菜味很重就算了，還沒好好照顧歐姆吧。。。</p>\n<p>果不其然，有天下過雨的晚上</p>\n<p>我帶歐姆去操場散步，</p>\n<p>牠突然興奮往前衝，等我走上前一看\ns\n我的天，你的狗鼻子平常什麼不嘟，現在嘟到一個不得了的小動物。。。。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/e1596/omupast4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"omu past\"\n        title=\"omu past\"\n        src=\"/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/1c72d/omupast4.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/a80bd/omupast4.jpg 148w,\n/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/1c91a/omupast4.jpg 295w,\n/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/1c72d/omupast4.jpg 590w,\n/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/a8a14/omupast4.jpg 885w,\n/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/fbd2c/omupast4.jpg 1180w,\n/static/1f74fc264dc90cb9f4a444d3bd5b79b6/e1596/omupast4.jpg 2048w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>是蟾蜍！！！！（尖叫））））））</p>\n<p>不是怕蟾蜍的尖叫，是歐姆嘴巴一直冒泡泡。。。。。</p>\n<p>當下趕快帶牠去沖水然後三步並作兩步衝去找獸醫解毒</p>\n<p>好險後來沒有大礙。。。。</p>\n<p>現在回顧有歐姆在身邊的日子，剛到我們家的那一年對歐姆來說應該是黯淡無光的吧。。。</p>\n<p>那時很少帶牠出去散步，下課回到家都累了懶了。。。 （（我真的很想搭時光機回去揍自己</p>\n<p>無法回到過去，那就在現在與未來好好的彌補與改善吧！！</p>\n<p>雖然，，，</p>\n<p>歐姆已經給自己找新媽媽了</p>\n<p>（（（未完待續。。。</p>","fields":{"slug":"/omupast/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"歐姆蛋是一隻狗","date":"August 18, 2020","description":"這篇是懺悔文。。。（下跪，上次跟室友聊起了以前無知的學生時期，發現我們真的很不適合養狗。","tags":["日記","歐姆蛋篇"],"images":[],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"src":"/static/d270baab8dbf425deb2c758d37dbdbb5/14b42/omupast1.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/omupast/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/sweethippo/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"貼心的小河馬","tags":["漫畫","小河馬篇"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/rabbitpants/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"我也要","tags":["漫畫","小河馬篇","滷蛋篇"]}}}}}